Triggered Actions Based on Call Conversations
To help your agents during calls, automatically trigger actions based on intelligence signals from your telephony system or keywords mentioned by agents or customers. For example, send the supervisor a notification when a customer uses profane language.

Reduce Agent Handling Time with Conversation Intelligence
title: Automating Contact Center with Triggered Actions
